

#  PROJECT: High-Availability Server-Based Order Processing Platform

Role: Linux Administrator | DevOps Engineer | SRE
Environment:
âœ” On-premises physical servers
âœ” Cloud-based VMs
âœ” No Kubernetes
âœ” Services running on Linux servers (systemd)
âœ” Nginx/HAProxy for traffic routing

---

# ğŸ“ 1. Project Overview (Plain English Summary)

I worked on building and maintaining a server-based production environment that powered an e-commerce order processing system.
All services ran directly on:

 Linux virtual machines
 Bare-metal servers
 With systemd as process manager

The platform supported:

 Public-facing APIs (user traffic)
 Internal service APIs (order, payment, inventory)
 Background worker servers
 Database cluster
 SAP Ariba enterprise integration

My role was to ensure:

 Uptime
 Scalability
 Security
 Monitoring
 Reliable deployments
 Performance tuning
 Incident response

---

